body.raw:
<soapenv:Envelope xmlns:soapenv="http://schemas.xmlsoap.org/soap/envelope/" xmlns:sup="http://webservices.hpi.co.uk/SupplementaryEnquiryV1">
   <soapenv:Header/>
   <soapenv:Body>
      <sup:ParameterizedEnquiryRequest xmlns="http://pat-wss.hpi.co.uk/TradeSoap/services/SupplementaryEnquiryV1?wsdl">
         <sup:Authentication>
            <!--Optional:-->
            <sup:ServiceVersion>
               <sup:MajorVersion>1</sup:MajorVersion>
               <sup:MinorVersion>16</sup:MinorVersion>
               <!--You may enter ANY elements at this point-->
            </sup:ServiceVersion>
            <sup:SubscriberDetails>
               <sup:CustomerCode>8733000</sup:CustomerCode>
               <sup:Initials>ABC</sup:Initials>
               <sup:Password>CAPTAIN</sup:Password>
               <!--You may enter ANY elements at this point-->
            </sup:SubscriberDetails>
            <!--You may enter ANY elements at this point-->
         </sup:Authentication>
         <sup:ParameterizedRequest>
            <sup:Asset>
               <!--Optional:-->
               <sup:Vrm>Y802HGX</sup:Vrm>
               <!--Optional:-->
               <!--sup:Vin>?</sup:Vin-->
               <!--Optional:-->
               <sup:Mileage>0</sup:Mileage>
               <!--Optional:-->
               <sup:Reference>?</sup:Reference>
            </sup:Asset>
            <sup:ParameterList>
               <!--Zero or more repetitions:-->
               <sup:Parameter>
                  <sup:Name>?</sup:Name>
                  <sup:Value>?</sup:Value>
               </sup:Parameter>
            </sup:ParameterList>
            <sup:PrimaryProduct>
               <sup:Code>HPI64</sup:Code>
               <!--You may enter ANY elements at this point-->
            </sup:PrimaryProduct>
            <!--Zero or more repetitions:-->
            <sup:SupplementaryProduct>
               <sup:Code>ADSMT</sup:Code>
               <!--You may enter ANY elements at this point-->
            </sup:SupplementaryProduct>
         </sup:ParameterizedRequest>
      </sup:ParameterizedEnquiryRequest>
   </soapenv:Body>
</soapenv:Envelope>
